	   <tr><td colspan=2>The only hitch I see in your combination is the issue of healing.&nbsp;&nbsp;How high do you plan to take your enchanter/tank team?  Will the majority of your xp come from your duo team or will it come from grouping with other people?  If the case is the later, then that's fine.  If the case is the former, then you might want to consider a druid or shaman.  Then you two will always be able to group together if you two can't find a group.  <br><br>The healing and buffing of both these hybrid classes mesh well with an enchanter's spells.  While a druid or shaman isn't very melee intensive, they do have some capacity in it at lower levels.<br><br>Some thoughts to think about...<br><br>Best Regards!<br><br>Calanctus of Sol Ro<br>lvl 60 Phantasmist<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
